<bibRefCitation author="Thaxter R." box="[444,606,848,874]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="397 - 414" refId="ref6991" refString="Thaxter R. 1901. Preliminary diagnoses of new species of Laboulbeniaceae. III. Proceedings of the American Academy of Arts and Sciences 36 (23): 397 - 414. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 20021631" type="journal article" year="1901">Thaxter 1901</bibRefCitation>
